{
 "fragments": [
  {
   "begin": "0.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "11.600", 
   "id": "s000001", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herr Pr\u00e4sident! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "11.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "15.480", 
   "id": "s000002", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Meine sehr verehrten Damen und Herren! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "15.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "23.320", 
   "id": "s000003", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Rechtsdurchsetzung f\u00fcr Verbraucher wird einer der Schwerpunkte in der Rechtspolitik der Gro\u00dfen Koalition sein. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "23.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "24.960", 
   "id": "s000004", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir k\u00fcmmern uns deswegen darum, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "24.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "30.360", 
   "id": "s000005", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "weil wir um die strukturelle Ungleichheit bei der Durchsetzung von Klein- "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "30.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "32.240", 
   "id": "s000006", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und Streusch\u00e4den wissen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "32.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "40.280", 
   "id": "s000007", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Der Zugang zum Recht ist oftmals erschwert durch die fehlende M\u00f6glichkeit, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "40.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "44.000", 
   "id": "s000008", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "direkt und einfach Recht zu bekommen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "44.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "45.120", 
   "id": "s000009", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "aber auch durch die H\u00fcrden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "45.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "48.680", 
   "id": "s000010", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die das aktuelle Zivilprozessrecht vorsieht. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "48.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "50.840", 
   "id": "s000011", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das wollen wir \u00e4ndern. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "50.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "51.880", 
   "id": "s000012", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir sagen: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "51.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "62.560", 
   "id": "s000013", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir wollen den Zugang zum Recht weiter erleichtern und gleichzeitig f\u00fcr die Gerichte die Voraussetzungen f\u00fcr die Anwendung des Rechts verbessern."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "62.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "64.360", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir wollen das deswegen tun, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "64.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "69.320", 
   "id": "s000015", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "weil die bisherigen Instrumente noch nicht vollst\u00e4ndig geeignet sind, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "69.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "71.880", 
   "id": "s000016", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "diese Ziele zu erf\u00fcllen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "71.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "80.400", 
   "id": "s000017", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Klagem\u00f6glichkeiten der Verb\u00e4nde nach dem Unterlassungsklagengesetz sind pr\u00e4ventiv und ein gutes Instrument, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "80.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "87.040", 
   "id": "s000018", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "um verbraucherfeindliche Klauseln gerade in den Bereichen Mobilfunk und Elektrizit\u00e4t zu unterbinden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "87.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "92.200", 
   "id": "s000019", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das Kapitalanleger-Musterverfahrensgesetz hat sich in der Praxis\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "92.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "93.760", 
   "id": "s000020", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "da m\u00fcssen wir ehrlich sein\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "93.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "96.840", 
   "id": "s000021", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "als zu schwerf\u00e4llig und zu langwierig erwiesen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "96.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "101.240", 
   "id": "s000022", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das zeigt beispielsweise das Verfahren um die Erstattung bei der Telekom, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "101.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "105.040", 
   "id": "s000023", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das sich jetzt mittlerweile \u00fcber ein Jahrzehnt zieht. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "105.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "110.240", 
   "id": "s000024", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Deswegen brauchen wir ein neues und ein gutes Instrument, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "110.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "116.520", 
   "id": "s000025", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "um die Anspr\u00fcche von Verbrauchern zu b\u00fcndeln und um Verbrauchern zu ihrem Recht zu verhelfen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "116.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "124.200", 
   "id": "s000026", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir stehen an der Seite der Verbraucher."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "124.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "126.720", 
   "id": "s000027", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Jetzt ist die Frage, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "126.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "136.040", 
   "id": "s000028", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ob der vorgeschlagene Gesetzentwurf der Kollegen von B\u00fcndnis\u00a090/Die Gr\u00fcnen diesem Ansinnen gerecht wird. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "136.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "141.280", 
   "id": "s000029", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir haben diesen Gesetzentwurf bereits mehrmals im Deutschen Bundestag debattiert."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "141.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "145.560", 
   "id": "s000030", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die grundlegenden juristischen Fragestellungen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "145.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "148.760", 
   "id": "s000031", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die dieser Gesetzentwurf aufwirft, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "148.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "150.760", 
   "id": "s000032", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "aber nicht beantwortet, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "150.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "152.200", 
   "id": "s000033", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "bleiben bestehen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "152.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "153.160", 
   "id": "s000034", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Frau Kollegin Rottmann, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "153.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "154.040", 
   "id": "s000035", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie haben gesagt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "154.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "156.680", 
   "id": "s000036", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "es d\u00fcrfe nicht auf das Geld ankommen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "156.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "157.720", 
   "id": "s000037", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ob jemand bei Klein- "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "157.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "160.680", 
   "id": "s000038", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "oder Streusch\u00e4den klagt oder nicht. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "160.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "163.200", 
   "id": "s000039", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wenn Sie aber von jemandem verlangen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "163.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "165.120", 
   "id": "s000040", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass er einen Anwalt nimmt\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "165.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "168.200", 
   "id": "s000041", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie wollen ja einen Anwaltszwang verankern\u00a0\u2013, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "168.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "175.880", 
   "id": "s000042", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dann muss er entweder die Erstberatungsgeb\u00fchr von \u00fcber 200\u00a0Euro aufbringen oder umst\u00e4ndlich erst einmal seine Rechtsschutzversicherung fragen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "175.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "177.200", 
   "id": "s000043", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ob er klagen darf."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "177.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "179.880", 
   "id": "s000044", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das ist kein einfacher Zugang zum Recht. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "179.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "183.000", 
   "id": "s000045", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie erschweren den Zugang zum Recht."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "183.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "184.640", 
   "id": "s000046", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie m\u00fcssen auch sehen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "184.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "188.680", 
   "id": "s000047", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "was mit \u00a7\u00a0619 Ihres Entwurfs bewirkt w\u00fcrde. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "188.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "191.760", 
   "id": "s000048", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Da f\u00fchren Sie einen sogenannten Gruppenkl\u00e4ger ein. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "191.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "197.280", 
   "id": "s000049", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Der Gruppenkl\u00e4ger soll f\u00fcr die Gruppe die entsprechenden Prozesshandlungen vornehmen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "197.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "198.400", 
   "id": "s000050", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das Problem ist aber, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "198.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "200.600", 
   "id": "s000051", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass Sie im gleichen Paragrafen sagen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "200.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "210.160", 
   "id": "s000052", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass dieser Gruppenkl\u00e4ger durch die anderen nicht in Haftung genommen werden kann und dass kein Schuldverh\u00e4ltnis begr\u00fcndet wird. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "210.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "211.280", 
   "id": "s000053", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das hei\u00dft \u00fcbersetzt: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "211.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "212.800", 
   "id": "s000054", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Der Gruppenkl\u00e4ger kann machen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "212.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "213.680", 
   "id": "s000055", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "was er will. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "213.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "216.120", 
   "id": "s000056", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das ist nicht verbraucherfreundlich."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "216.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "217.720", 
   "id": "s000057", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie m\u00fcssen bitte auch sehen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "217.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "224.640", 
   "id": "s000058", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "was f\u00fcr eine komplizierte Regelung in \u00a7\u00a0623 bez\u00fcglich der Frage des Vergleiches vorgesehen ist. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "224.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "226.560", 
   "id": "s000059", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Demnach soll ein Vergleich nur zustande kommen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "226.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "229.800", 
   "id": "s000060", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn weniger als 30\u00a0Prozent den Austritt aus dem Vergleich erkl\u00e4ren. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "229.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "232.120", 
   "id": "s000061", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Warum haben Sie es nicht andersherum gel\u00f6st und festgelegt: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "232.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "233.720", 
   "id": "s000062", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "\u201eWenn 50\u00a0Prozent beitreten, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "233.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "234.680", 
   "id": "s000063", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dann gilt der Vergleich\u201c? "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "234.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "238.280", 
   "id": "s000064", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das w\u00e4re eine wesentlich einfachere Regelung gewesen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "238.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "246.320", 
   "id": "s000065", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Schlie\u00dflich sind auch die Regelungen \u00fcber die Berufung ziemlich kompliziert und verbraucherfeindlich. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "246.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "248.920", 
   "id": "s000066", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Der Gruppenkl\u00e4ger kann n\u00e4mlich Berufung einlegen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "248.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "251.000", 
   "id": "s000067", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "auch mit Wirkung f\u00fcr die Gruppe, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "251.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "255.400", 
   "id": "s000068", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ohne dass jemand aus der Gruppe irgendwie aus der Berufung austreten kann. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "255.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "260.880", 
   "id": "s000069", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Damit erh\u00f6hen Sie das Prozesskostenrisiko f\u00fcr die gesamte Gruppe auf Kosten derjenigen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "260.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "263.880", 
   "id": "s000070", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die eigentlich nur eine Erstattung der Streusch\u00e4den wollen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "263.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "267.760", 
   "id": "s000071", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Insofern ist Ihr Gesetzentwurf zu kompliziert, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "267.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "270.840", 
   "id": "s000072", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "baut zu hohe H\u00fcrden auf und kann den Anspruch, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "270.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "273.840", 
   "id": "s000073", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Rechtsdurchsetzung f\u00fcr den Verbraucher zu verbessern, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "273.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "274.840", 
   "id": "s000074", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "nicht erf\u00fcllen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "274.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "276.360", 
   "id": "s000075", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Deswegen lehnen wir Ihren Gesetzentwurf ab\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "276.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "278.440", 
   "id": "s000076", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "aus inhaltlichen Gr\u00fcnden."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "278.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "282.080", 
   "id": "s000077", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Meine Damen und Herren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "282.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "289.200", 
   "id": "s000078", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wir werden als Gro\u00dfe Koalition alsbald einen Gesetzentwurf zur Musterfeststellungsklage vorlegen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "289.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "291.040", 
   "id": "s000079", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie werden erkennen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "291.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "294.160", 
   "id": "s000080", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass damit der Zugang zum Recht wesentlich erleichtert wird."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "294.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "297.600", 
   "id": "s000081", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es werden nur anerkannte Verb\u00e4nde klagebefugt sein, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "297.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "301.600", 
   "id": "s000082", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "es wird ein sehr niederschwelliges Klageregister geben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "301.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "306.360", 
   "id": "s000083", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und wir wollen auch die Verfahrensfristen verk\u00fcrzen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "306.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "313.680", 
   "id": "s000084", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "damit die Durchsetzung des Rechts anders als im Kapitalanleger-Musterverfahrensgesetz nicht Monate oder Jahre dauert.\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "316.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "318.040", 
   "id": "s000085", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich w\u00fcrde die Zwischenfrage zulassen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "318.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "319.200", 
   "id": "s000086", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herr Pr\u00e4sident."
   ]
  }, 
  {
